thread.title: TV | Second Captains Live

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | Second Captains Live
text: It's a Second Captains special tonight ahead of Ireland's Rugby World Cup quarter-final against Argentina tomorrow, and the lads are taking the show outside of Ireland for the very first time as they broadcast live from Cardiff. No doubt there will be a great buzz in the studio while it's set to feature guests from across the world of Rugby.
